{"tid":559200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國軍人好似想呃我錢(終於唔係金融雞佳佳)","createTime":"2018-02-13T03:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T14:01:28.000Z","uid":125576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1db9f456cd5e88e677f3695bc5de16f2e053f099","tid":559200,"uid":125576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"今朝扮工果陣 有個Facebook friend邀請<br />\n係一個無共同朋友嘅鬼佬 <br />\n佢facebook入面淨係得啲耶L野 like都唔多個<br />\n直覺同我講係騙案 扮工期間終於有啲野做<br />\n<br />\n背景： 美國軍人 老婆cancer死左 有一個十歲嘅女<br />\no係緊敘利亞執行緊啲維護和平任務<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/111527_2f35e64723d90a0cc94569c48b3a8d78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F111527_2f35e64723d90a0cc94569c48b3a8d78.jpg&h=3115183c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(原諒我啲I go to school by bus英文）<br />\n一黎就話覺得我look good同caring lady <br />\n但我block哂啲FB啲野 icon都係得背面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後一路嘅對話都係dear dear dear dear <br />\n又問我係唔係單身啊 又係咁god bless又係咁叫我pray<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/112150_e1efede362ecb93dfef7300a741246d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F112150_e1efede362ecb93dfef7300a741246d5.jpg&h=d9f665f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前都見好多網上扮美軍再呃錢嘅騙案<br />\n所以我一野就問佢 佢之後就嬲豬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/112511_cb3ed626e53a86ef3bd7b0c615d34bda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F112511_cb3ed626e53a86ef3bd7b0c615d34bda.jpg&h=0c062aba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後再問我拎wechat 但條友又話自己美國人<br />\n但我wechat search佢 佢個region係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/112805_61886c676dd2ff88117dd36ad2441971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F112805_61886c676dd2ff88117dd36ad2441971.jpg&h=dece4031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問佢點解佢話係香港整嘅個wechat<br />\n奇奇怪怪 之後我話 我唔常用wechat 有咩呢到傾<br />\n佢就話唔得閒 係office好忙 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/13/113305_577211247c1cbf0b3bdb9a1e7b710d50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F13%2F113305_577211247c1cbf0b3bdb9a1e7b710d50.jpg&h=bca58f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又會咁岩係個美國軍人 咁岩又喪偶 又咁岩有個女 <br />\n又又咁岩係敘利亞進行任務 同新聞講嘅一樣<br />\n<br />\n自問唔識玩 有無人代勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090defd9d5cb23f2df0966528195e3bfd744539c","tid":559200,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"321284416278f63ca8857e62e42350e64b22cd5f","tid":559200,"uid":8717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"佢啲英文好正"},{"pid":"fb144220488f9bbed2e5f72bf7efeb8d9692491f","tid":559200,"uid":125576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"090defd9d5cb23f2df0966528195e3bfd744539c","tid":559200,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"佢又上水啦"},{"pid":"8e2f87d09f7c2c8edc25ab343bdab680e69723af","tid":559200,"uid":125576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"321284416278f63ca8857e62e42350e64b22cd5f","tid":559200,"uid":8717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"佢啲英文好正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"I go to school by bus"}]}